pageContext.claim: “There was no collusion, and that’s been so found, as you know, by the House Intelligence Committee.  There’s no collusion.  There was no collusion with Russia, other than by the Democrats — or, as I call them, the “obstructionists,” because they truly are obstructionists.”
pageContext.analysis: The House Intelligence Committee report was Republican-only. The special prosecutor has reach no such conclusion. There is no evidence that Democrats "colluded" with Russian and in fact the Democratic National Committee was the subject of Russian attacks.
